# Lab 02: Ground Segment & Telemetry Integration

## Objective
Establish a reliable telemetry link between the physical sensor (DHT22) and a cloud-based dashboard (ThingSpeak) using a Raspberry Pi 4 as a gateway.

## Progress
- **Sensor Integration:** Interfaced DHT22 sensor with Raspberry Pi GPIO (Pin 7).
- **Environment Management:** Implemented Python virtual environments to ensure dependency isolation and system stability.
- **Data Pipeline:** Configured secure HTTPS transmission to ThingSpeak API.
- **Resilience:** Implemented exception handling for checksum and buffer stability during RF/signal interference.

## Hardware Connections
| DHT22 Pin | Pi Pin | Function |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| Pin 1 | Pin 1 | 3.3V |
| Pin 2 | Pin 7 | GPIO 4 |
| Pin 4 | Pin 9 | GND |

